// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL4-5_Task_02 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Promoter 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3178177380" "You know, when I put the call out for superheroes, I didn't think *YOU* were going to be the one to show, I mean, did you come back to life JUST for this? I'm gonna be the talk of the town now!  Now I hear you sayin' you wanna be my #1 Star today.  I gotta tell you... my day's gettin' better and better!"
// Answer Text :
"P2648988276" "How much is the winner's purse?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P4177496290" "The purse?  I didn't think you did this kinda thing for money. I guess dying and coming back to life CAN leave a guy poor.<br><br>Then again, I never thought in my wildest dreams you would be my top prizefighter, either.  So I guess don't go looking a reincarnated Greek God in the mouth, right?<br><br>With your name on the bill, I'll be rolling in the dough - which, if you win you'll get a very, very modest percentage, of course.<br><br>But hey, you know your street rep is gonna go down the can, right?"
// Answer Text :
"P185488956" "I died once, I think I can handle something like my reputation."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2997170833" "I gotta say, there are times I wonder about you and that attitude of yours. "
// Answer Text :
"P279036554" "Hey, don't forget how I’m always Holier-Than-Thou, too!"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P4020761373" "Yeah, you got that right -"
// Answer Text :
"P2156152956" "And I get up in people's faces for no good reason."
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P1422778431" "Yup!  You sure do that -"
// Answer Text :
"P3246139494" "And I'm really mean to {HeroName} even though {HeroName} is way cooler than me."
// Page InformationPage5 Text :
"P290541019" "{HeroName}?  What's that idiot got to do with -"
// Answer Text :
"P1086388376" "And I'm all stuffy and I talk like I've got a stick up -"
// Page InformationPage6 Text :
"P2882908745" "So, hey, States!<br><br>I'm gonna need you to get warmed up - give the audience a taste of what's in store, you know?<br><br>I've got a guy waiting to get the snot beat outta him, so why don't you head on over there and show the boys what you can do."
// Answer Text :
"P1334933822" "I'm on it, after all, I -am- Statesman."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P863814727" "After looking around your place, you find a mask that looks just like the one Statesman used to wear.  If you grab some spandex or pantyhose (or whatever it is that he wore), you can throw together a costume that looks like his in no time.  Once you've got that out of the way, you can show up to the fight acting like him.  Everyone will think you're Statesman, back from the dead!  No harm, no foul, and even better - no blame coming back on you!"
// AcceptString :
"P1559043543" "Put together a Statesman costume for the fight!"
// SendOffString :
"P3012019579" "This costume was even easier than you had originally thought.  Geeeeeez... at least *you* spend some time trying to throw together a costume that's stylish unlike this get-up.<br><br> Well, now you'll look like Statesman, so get down there to that fight and rake in the big bucks!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2918061980" "Enter the fight as Statesman!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P842751897" "If you plan on making some cash from that costume, you need to get to that fight - Pronto!"
// TaskTitle :
"P510557126" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Good Beating</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3997872058" "This looks like the place on the invitation.  Let's hope it's not too late to put your name on the brackets!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3432927055" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Good Beating</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to walk out of that trap alive, and no one found out that you weren't really Statesman.  However, you DID get an odd email later from someone you don't know:<br><br>'Smart thinking, you posing as Statesman to trigger Stardusk's trap. Try it again, and you'll have the Phalanx to deal with it. Let the man rest in peace."
