// DetailString :
"P1828203183" "This is the key to the safe with all the cash.  The cash you weren't told about.  The cash that no one suspects you would be involved in the theft of it if it mysteriously went missing.  You know... while you were disabling the security system."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - GasTankDestroyed 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3753813399" "Proof of Gas Tank Destroyed"
// DetailString :
"P3250568542" "You have destroyed the gas tank with the payload for the security system.  This should buy you enough time to get to that safe before the heroes finish doing their job."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SafeOpened 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2210232185" "Receipt for the Security System"
// DetailString :
"P871737203" "You look at the reciept and see a number of notes that shows how to rig it so that it spreads a poison gas if turned off.  If any damage happens to the system, though, it will release a sleeping gas automatically throughout the building.  Wait!  It was a trap from the beginning!  Those Longbow guys may not have been killed due to your passive-aggressive actions, but they've been knocked out and are completely defenseless!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2320423100" "Looks like if you don't take this seriously, you're going to be in a world of hurt to say the least.  It's in your best interests for Longbow to not go sifting through your past too deeply.  And as much as you don't like the 'friendly reminder' that Manticore gave you, your only other alternative would be to high-tail it back to the Rogue Isles... and never return."
// AcceptString :
"P3389835066" "Follow Manticore's instructions... Reluctantly."
// SendOffString :
"P3549259873" "The assignment seems simple enough.  You are to sneak in through the back and disable the primary security system.  Details have been shown what it looks like, and it seems simple enough - just push the big red button that has the words 'Don't Push' on it.  You've always been curious about those kinds of buttons..."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1839546888" "Push that button..."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3693324436" "Manticore's threat is not something to be taken lightly. The assignment seems simple enough.  You are to to sneak in through the back and disable the primary security system. Details have been shown what it looks like, and it seems simple enough - just push the big red button that has the words 'Don't Push' on it.  You've always been curious about those kinds of buttons..."
// TaskTitle :
"P2493121421" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Compromising Photograph</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3611937603" "Now that you think of it... they only told you that you had to disable the system, not specifically push the button.  If you're going to be forced into helping Longbow, why not blow whole damned thing up?  Plus... there's something odd about that 'DON'T PUSH' button..."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3853436982" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Compromising Photograph</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>After much congratulations on part of Longbow, you come to the conclusion that Manticore held up his end of the bargain and didn't turn in the evidence.  For the time being, you're in the clear.<br><br>However...<br><br>While running around Paragon, you come across a picture taped to the wall of you opening the Warriors' safe and pocketing the cash..."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1384218033" "Ugh... So... Tired... *snore*"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1392275929" "Warrior Rearguard"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P917689581" "Okay, we gotta keep an eye on the back door."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2648749094" "{HeroName}?  Longbow gotcha you working for them now?  Man, that's low... even for you."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P386844191" "You know what those hero types are like, right? They're always gettin in everyone's business."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2055803109" "Did they even tell you why they're raiding us?  Nah... they don't even trust you, do they?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2655312608" "Yeah, they didn't want you sniffing around for the cash.<em t=3>Well, they're gonna be reeeal surprised when they find out I'm the only one with the key to the safe."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2658220712" "Sucks that you're here.  Big Brutus thought that someone would push that button for sure."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2332091759" "...wanted to see it set off..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2985891097" "You ain't so tough!"

