// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2021469224" "{HeroName}?  What in the heck are you doing...<em t=3> You... YOUUUUUU!<em t=3>YOU blew up my security system! You're going to pay for that!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P2760012477" "Do you know how much that cost me?!<em t=3>I'm ruined! BECAUSE OF YOU!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
