// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1337432259" "Man...<em t=3>I still can't believe you blew it up!!!<em t=3>You were supposed to push the red button that said push me!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3554759660" "What's this world coming to... {HeroName}... a hero... <em t=3>Yeah, right...."
