// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL4-5_Task_05 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - LegacyLeaderOne 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2032829789" "The Oculus said you would come and join us in our time of need and it was correct.  I was the one who sent you the message.  Now that you're here, you can join our order and help us defend our treasures from these slag golems that are attacking us."
// Answer Text :
"P2559057334" "I'm not joining - err... treasures?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2428663164" "Yes, every initiate is given access to view the future.  Whoever is behind the slag golems wants the Oculus so that they, too, can see the future."
// Answer Text :
"P542576405" "So I have to join to use this?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P4025624924" "Yes.  Once you join you can access the Oculus.  But that is for another time.  We've been suffering great losses and I don't know if we can hold out any longer.  So will you join us forever?"
// Answer Text :
"P1673900490" "Oh, totally, like, yeah - Where's the Oculus?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P2976762598" "The Oculus is kept here within the heart of the caves.  However, we must make it to the end of the caves to defend the next breach.  We need the help of your unique powers there.  I will meet you there.  You might see the Oculus along the way, but don't pay attention to it.  We may even have to give our lives to preserve all of our secrets!"
// Answer Text :
"P770218124" "Yeah, lives... I'll totally see you back there!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - LegacyLeaderTwo 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2981220939" "You may be wondering what is going on.  The Oculus showed us the future, and the future was for you to be tested.  All of this was just a test to see if you were the one in our vision."
// Answer Text :
"P990338720" "Your vision?  What in the hell is going on?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P738541357" "It no longer matters, for you are the one.  The Oculus you stole from us is but a shard of the True One.  You have passed and are granted the right to view from it."
// Answer Text :
"P3663409544" "Granted?  Tell me now what's going on!"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P738602094" "I cannot just yet.  It is not yet time.  But know that you are to be rewarded for your deed.  There is another chest, and within it is a larger shard.  You shall now see the future."
// Answer Text :
"P3162972029" "Really?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P156130078" "Yes, really this time.  And I shall see to it that our controlled slag golems will not molest you any more."
// Answer Text :
"P2821837755" "Okay..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - TheOculus 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3176361538" "The Vision of the Oculus"
// DetailString :
"P202093212" "When you look into the Oculus, you see a vision of slag golems pounding the bodies of the Legacy Chain into a pulp.  They lay dead everywhere, looking off expectantly at a shadowy figure in the distance.  You realize if you don't help them, they'll all die like dogs, waiting for you to come to thier aid... though you're planning on never coming to their aid.  That's just downright...well, jacked, for lack of a better word. <br><br>Go save them!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P825017153" "Something about this seems fishy.  But then again, you're not one to be caught off guard.  And you're also not one to walk away from a gamble.  And you're ESPECIALLY not one to walk away from free treasure - even if it is from some creepy guy who has an eyeball for a head.<br><br>If this *is* some elaborate trap, you know you'd be able to work your way out of it somehow.  On the other hand, if you ignore this chance to be handed over a handful of shinies...well, maybe you don't deserve to call yourself a rogue."
// AcceptString :
"P158949330" "Risk it!"
// SendOffString :
"P3145552965" "You try to remember more of your dream - you know, just in case there ARE people with eyeball heads.  All you can remember about it is the path you walked to get to the caves.<br><br>That's probably the best place to start looking, wouldn't you say?"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P615375480" "Collect your treasure!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1500505553" "If you're going to get your hands on the free treasure, you had best get moving!  You try to remember more of your dream - you know, just in case there ARE people with eyeball heads.  All you can remember about it is the path you walked to get to the caves.<br><br>That's probably the best place to start looking, wouldn't you say?"
// TaskTitle :
"P3725665518" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Nocturnal Oneiromancies</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3681974421" "Well, these sure do look like the same caves in your dreams.  Now to see if you've been set up."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1819070275" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Nocturnal Oneiromancies</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You vaguely remember... something - <br><br>Gazing into the Oculus... <br><br>Seeing yourself standing among the heroes of Paragon City as a friend... <br><br>Seeing yourself... as one of them. <br><br>Watching a sense of pride in your face... one which you haven't seen in a mirror for a long time..."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P3481263075" "Speal with the Lucid Oneiromancer"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P3196839725" "Lucid Oneiromancer"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P669505515" "Foul beast, you shall never have the divining Oculus!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2894696774" "As the Oculus foretold, you are here, {HeroName}! Assist me in my hour of need!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1331722243" "Slag Golem Homonculus"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3132301621" "OCCCC...UUUUUUU...LUSSS..."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P1389131324" "We have much to discuss, {HeroName}.  Quickly, before the rest arrive."
// Script Variable WaveShout :
"P998412498" "{HeroName} is still here! Get {Hero.gender=Male him|her}!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P3465667564" "Do not tarry! I'll meet you at the back of the caves!"

