// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_RogToHero_SL4-5_Task_06 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - MissThystle 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1720947190" "You know, I'm thinking I might have to lower your cut on this gig.  I've been the one doing all this work here, you know."
// Answer Text :
"P1108048274" "Shut your trap and give me my cash, Thystle."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3669174580" "What?! Oh no no NO!...<br><br>You're not getting paid until the WHOLE job is done, got it?  Don't think you can fool me the way you're fooling all those heroes."
// Answer Text :
"P1344564032" "Wait... There's more to the job?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3364817588" "Of course there is!  You didn't read the whole email, did you?!<br><br>Look, you got little Polar-Wolar under the Lost's sway and - uh - I handled the mercs hired to rescue her, right?  Now we do the real job, got it?  We hold off any other rescue attempts while the Lost transform that poor wittle giwl into a breeding host to create genetically modified... well, i don't know what they are.<br><br>Look - All I know is that when they're done with her, she'll be popping out those creatures like an Octo-mom or something.  But you know what I care about? All I care about is ALL the CASH they're offering me - er... - us, I meant - to do this."
// Answer Text :
"P3519617051" "Hold on!  They're going to turn her into a... breeding machine?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1624496840" "Oh don't start getting all high and mighty on me now, {HeroName}.  I know perfectly well what kinds of things you've been up to in the Rogue Isles.  Just because you're hanging out with heroes Doesn't - Mean - You - Are- One.<br><br>You'll never be heroic, {HeroName} got it?  You're a sick, disgusting mongrel like all the rest of us.  Once you start acting like you're more than dirt is when one of those heroes comes along and makes you look real stupid, you know.<br><br>Now listen up... if you go back on our deal, I'll get Arachnos down your throat.<br><br>AND you won't get your half of the cut!"
// Answer Text :
"P26958701" "But... I was never THAT bad..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - AdministerSerum 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2399762365" "Polar Shift's Willing Compliance"
// DetailString :
"P3151584069" "You've administered the serum that you were given by Miss Thystle.  Apparently Polar Shift is now under her control or something and off to wherever it is that she's supposed to go.  Whatever.  Now get your money from Thystle."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P15374425" "You know that you can't really trust Miss Thystle.  But that's what you can trust about her - she's untrustworthy.  However, she knows not to go back on a deal - everyone worth their salt knows bad things happen to people who back out on deals.  And for some spare cash, it might be worth it.<br><br>The thing that sells you the most about the job is that you get to knock Polar Shift down a peg or two.  It seems all you have to do is lure her to some caves below and hit her with some of Thystle's numbing toxin to make her all giddy and dumb.<br><br>Heh... make Miss Priss act giddy and stupid?  You're in!"
// AcceptString :
"P2600363133" "Do this easy job and make some fast cash!"
// SendOffString :
"P4253514861" "You agree to the job and get the details of when and where to meet with Polar Shift in tow.  Seems Thystle is working with those weirdos, the Lost.  She's given you a vial of her chlorotoxins to use on Polar Shift.<br><br>Stick her with the needle, and you're done.  This should go smoothly."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P243474760" "Knock Polar Shift down a peg!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1650775790" "If you wanna get paid, you're gonna need to get Polar Shift over to those caves.  Thystle has given you a vial of her chlorotoxins to use on Polar Shift.<br><br>Stick her with the needle, and you're done.  This should go smoothly."
// TaskTitle :
"P4206861149" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Under-the-Table Job</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3550427711" "Well, that was easy enough.  You lured Polar Shift here under the pretense of 'saving' some baby seals inside the caves.  It took you forever to ditch her friend, Flambeaux.  The hothead was threatening to call the 'police' the whole time... Even though she's a super, herself.  What an airhead."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1295730707" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Under-the-Table Job</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Even though you didn't get paid for that job, it doesn't matter, okay?  What they had planned for her is something even that stuck up Queen Bee doesn't deserve.<br><br>But the thing she said to you at the end? Well, it's kinda weighing on your - lack! - of conscience...<br><br> Hero?"
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P2718152030" "Talk to Miss Thystle"
// Script Variable PET_NAME :
"P890628734" "Polar Shift"
// Script Variable PET_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2098688939" "That sound... It's... Confusing me...."
// Script Variable PET_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P781711742" "Who... Who's there?"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P779011542" "What... What did you do to me?"
// Script Variable SayOnArrival :
"P2932158907" "I have to fight... The... The music... It's calling me..."
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveText :
"P2348957143" "Ambush Polar Shift and administer the serum"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2525798658" "Sky Raider Rescue Team"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1195497664" "We've got to get her out of here! She's not looking so good."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P988822754" "{HeroName}?  You're in on this?  But... but i thought you were going straight..."
// Script Variable WaveShout :
"P1936714319" "<shout>Stop {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P3609192693" "{HeroName}, it's you."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2409989984" "Now we fight"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P892451606" "I die!"

