// Objective - ScriptKidnapPolarShift 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P3652454421" "Miss Thystle"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3241343543" "Where in the hell is {HeroName}?  {HeroName}!!!  I'm in a bit of some trouble here!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1096561667" "There you are!  If you want your money, get over here and help me!"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1531472054" "Look, lady - we're being paid to get her to safety.  We'll take down anyone else in on your operation for free if you get in our way."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2790095863" "Bring it, {HeroName}, bring it."
