// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SecurityCaptain 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3735530418" "Go ahead, just take everything.  It's not like I really need this job.  Eating is so overrated."
// Answer Text :
"P2626950589" "I found this loot and am bringing it back."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2237401756" "What?  You're bringing it back?  Why in the hell would you do that?"
// Answer Text :
"P1696750302" "This artifact belongs in a museum - or rich collector's home."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P4099730433" "I am completely lost.  You didn't steal it, but you're bringing it back?  Then why didn't you just turn it in when you found it?"
// Answer Text :
"P1003968744" "Look, I've got a rep to maintain, okay?"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1895927287" "Ahhh... I think I'm catching on.  You don't want people to know you're actually a softie deep down inside, right?  Like a cuddly little teddy bear?  Feel bad for all that stuff you used to -"
// Answer Text :
"P1263205903" "Shut up NOW or I kill you.  Pick one."
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P281584220" "*ahem*... okay, look, this is what I'll do.  You put everything back around where it once was and I'll tell the boys to leave you alone.  Once it's back, I'll set off the alarm to get some heroes here, and they'll never know it was you."
// Answer Text :
"P605438318" "Sounds good. Let's do this."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3961572936" "You just watched a news report detailing the theft of this painting from the highly secured administrative offices of a well known, high class auction house.  The way it was stolen was an amazing story unto itself, but that it was stolen before tomorrow's auction for charity was even more audacious.  This proceeds of this painting was to be used to rescue kittens from the animal shelter and given to the children at Saint Maria's Home for Orphans with Life-Threatening Illnesses.<br><br>Okay... now that you think about it...<br><br>If you sell this painting on the black market, it's entirely possible you'll also be purchasing a one-way ticket to a very, very hot place.  Sure, you may have a lot of those tickets already, but we're talking Business Class here."
// AcceptString :
"P1152017600" "Give the painting back... FAST!"
// SendOffString :
"P3694729955" "It's not going to be that easy.  You don't know where the driver is, and after delivering the package to you, it's possible you don't even know *IF* the driver *IS*.<br><br>So... There's only one way to go about this.  You're going to need to break into the auction house...<br><br>...and RETURN the painting!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3240710691" "Return the stolen painting to the auction house!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1329433015" "If you want that painting to have its chance to help nuns get the dying orphaned kids those little kittens to make their lives better and - <br><br>*sniff sniff* <br><br>- Look... just get to that auction house, okay!?"
// TaskTitle :
"P3894443471" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Disproportionate Package</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1688564008" "Lets hope this is the right office or all your work will be wasted.  Find the guard captain and 'convince' him to let you return the work without being identified."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2134037541" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Disproportionate Package</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Not only were you able to return the artwork, you were also able to crack a couple of skulls and erase all the videotapes of you even being there."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P2615879265" "Talk to the Security Captain"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P618851075" "Auction House Security Captain"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4112220933" "Stay on alert guys!<br><br>After we lost that painting several days ago, we can't afford to lose anything else.  I hope you new guys have learned from your mistakes."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3436270523" "Oh no... Not again..."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3045523551" "Security Officer Temp"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1897148161" "HEY!  It wasn't our fault, you know what I'm sayin'?<br><br>It was just dumb luck."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3589263507" "Hey!  You're ear - I mean...<br><br>HEY! We got an intruder!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P4025024084" "Go ahead.  Just clock me on the back of the head like you did last time.<br><br>Let's get it over with.<br><br>Oh... You want to taunt me first I see."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1129329720" "Okay, let's go over to the Security intercom so we can announce a breakin.  After that, you can hightail it outta the place."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2456318816" "Okay, the alarms are now going off.  You'll want to get out of here now.  And if you need to crack a couple of skulls, hey, I saw nothing, you know?"

