// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P849877081" "If this information is true and arachnos has taken over a whole police station, that really sucks.  I mean, it's one thing to be able to boss people around because you act all high and mighty, and it's another thing to be 'legally' allowed to do it!  And all these heroes have secret identities, too.  I mean, c'mon... some of us don't wear masks just because they look cool.  I mean, how can you go to the grocery store if everyone wants autographs, know what I'm saying?"
// AcceptString :
"P2569343352" "Destroy the Arachnos secret identity information!"
// SendOffString :
"P573019975" "Since this message you got looks nothing like a trap, you should be able to just sneak into the police station, erase the files, and no one will be the wiser!  What could possibly go wrong?"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2395628556" "Destroy those secret files!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2657684836" "There's no time like the present to do this.  You best get your butt runnin!"
