// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1277644412" "If this book actually is what it claims to be, then you can probably get your hands on some sweet digs.  And it seems that everyone likes a guy wearing old-fashioned armor - just look at that Positron guy!  Though it sounds maaaaaaybe a bit dangerous, you can't really pass up this chance at getting a costume that will put you on the same level as Synapse."
// AcceptString :
"P3729780076" "Get that Armor!"
// SendOffString :
"P3434191889" "According to this book, you're going to need to travel really far below in some hidden areas.  After that, you'll need to find some magic words or something on some tablets, then get some godlike things to follow you around.  Then open the coffin of an ancient -something - take it's armor and taaaaddaaaa!  Super Positron!  Sounds easy."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1903984621" "Recover the Ancient Armor"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1972100832" "If you're ever going to be as cool as Positron, you're going to need to get down to that ancient city - pronto!"
// TaskTitle :
"P3545075436" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Long Protected Armor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3049485578" "This looks like the pictures in the book.  First thing you're going to need to do is find one of those tablets."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2218802832" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Long Protected Armor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You can't believe it.  Seriously, you reallllly can't believe it.  This was one of the very few times you had a real shot at being on the level of someone like Positron - at least to the public eye - and that gunfreak Hollow Point screwed it all up for you!  Now where are you going to get your hands on old crap like that puffed-up power armor guy has!  Man, that Hollow Point seriously owes you."
